parameters: \SE[2] There's a lookout over there too...

\SE[2]If we're found, we won't be able to avoid a battle, right?
[1]There's no way to take a detour either...
\i[385] I obtained the Magical Care Alpha! \$
\SE[2]There's a bonfire in a place like this...

By touching the bonfire, you can completely restore your health.
There are no restrictions, so let's take a rest when we're
exhausted.

Also, you can save anytime from the 'menu screen'. We recommend
saving frequently and in multiple slots.
